to Detroit.

2761
02:41:17,614 --> 02:41:19,104
Well.

2762
02:41:19,182 --> 02:41:21,412
That's grand news.

2763
02:41:21,485 --> 02:41:22,884
That's right.

2764
02:41:22,953 --> 02:41:25,547
That's right.
We're very happy about it.

2765
02:41:27,624 --> 02:41:28,886
I'll take that, ma'am.

2766
02:41:28,959 --> 02:41:30,551
Thank you, John.

2767
02:41:31,461 --> 02:41:33,861
Shouldn't we telephone
the boys about the wedding?

2768
02:41:33,930 --> 02:41:35,557
Oh, they'll be in class.

2769
02:41:35,632 --> 02:41:37,361
That's right.

2770
02:41:37,434 --> 02:41:40,130
Better wait until this evening.

2771
02:41:50,480 --> 02:41:53,381
- It's been a long time...
- We should let Aunt Mary know.

2772
02:41:54,651 --> 02:41:57,643
- What was that, Cordelia?
- I was thinking.

2773
02:41:57,721 --> 02:42:02,317
Maybe we could do some traveling
now that the children are all...

2774
02:42:02,392 --> 02:42:03,723
That's a good idea.

2775
02:42:03,794 --> 02:42:05,421
I've always wanted to travel.

2776
02:42:05,495 --> 02:42:08,555
We can go to Detroit
and see Cordy and Angie.

2777
02:42:08,932 --> 02:42:11,526
Oh, Anthony.

2778
02:42:12,002 --> 02:42:13,264
Yeah.

2779
02:42:25,615 --> 02:42:29,346
<i>? Let them go, let them go?</i>

2780
02:42:29,419 --> 02:42:33,287
<i>? Let them try their wings?</i>

2781
02:42:33,356 --> 02:42:40,387
<i>? Little birds were born
to fly?</i>

2782
02:42:40,464 --> 02:42:48,337
<i>? Not until they roam
can they miss their home?</i>

2783
02:42:48,405 --> 02:42:55,743
<i>? And it won't be long
till Christmas?</i>

2784
02:42:59,683 --> 02:43:03,517
<i>? When the branches are bare?</i>

2785
02:43:03,587 --> 02:43:07,148
<i>? The December air?</i>

2786
02:43:07,224 --> 02:43:14,562
<i>? Comes alive
with frost and pine?</i>

2787
02:43:14,631 --> 02:43:18,567
<i>? And they'll yearn to be?</i>

2788
02:43:18,635 --> 02:43:22,366
<i>? By the family tree?</i>

2789
