till Christmas?</i>

2790
02:43:30,514 --> 02:43:34,075
<i>? The years go by?</i>

2791
02:43:34,151 --> 02:43:37,814
<i>? And every night?</i>

2792
02:43:37,888 --> 02:43:44,817
<i>? You say, "Sweet dreams,
sleep tight"?</i>

2793
02:43:45,862 --> 02:43:53,997
<i>? Then comes the day
you're forced to say?</i>

2794
02:43:55,038 --> 02:43:57,598
<i>? "Don't forget to write"?</i>

2795
02:44:02,979 --> 02:44:07,416
<i>? There'll be holly
and popcorn?</i>

2796
02:44:07,484 --> 02:44:10,749
<i>? And mistletoe?</i>

2797
02:44:10,821 --> 02:44:17,886
<i>? There'll be songs
by fireglow?</i>

