2855
02:47:36,159 --> 02:47:38,024
<i>? When the truth
is nobly spoken?</i>

2856
02:47:38,094 --> 02:47:40,221
<i>? It's respect
you've got to pay?</i>

2857
02:47:40,296 --> 02:47:42,264
<i>? So fill your cup
and lift it up?</i>

2858
